			 (24)</cato:entity-ref>—</text>
						<subparagraph id="H69E5287C1FF54F9782500EB2EB7B2EBB">
              <enum>(A)</enum>
              <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Older Americans Act of 1965/s:102/p:24/sp:B">subparagraph
